{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_34","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed for `org.glassfish.jersey.core:jersey-client:2.25.1`.\n\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2637-library-new-request-org.glassfish.jersey.core-jersey-client-2.25.1-058ef453\n\nThe most likely failing stage was native verification after partial test generation, not artifact discovery. The focused test appears to have reached the targeted dynamic-access sites (`4/4`, `100.00%`), but `logs/org.glassfish.jersey.core:jersey-client:2.25.1/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-08T18-18-19-810557Z.log` shows native test failure in `HttpUrlConnectorAnonymous5Test` with `java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: org.glassfish.jersey.client.JerseyClientBuilder` from `ClientBuilder.newClient()`. The follow-up trace run in `logs/org.glassfish.jersey.core:jersey-client:2.25.1/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-06-08T18-19-15-468208Z.log` then reports `MissingReflectionRegistrationError` for `org.osgi.framework.BundleReference`, which points to missing Jersey bootstrap/runtime metadata beyond the original `HttpUrlConnector$5` coverage target. A separate environment problem also blocked regeneration: `logs/org.glassfish.jersey.core:jersey-client:2.25.1/native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-2026-06-08T18-19-14-426573Z.log` fails because `native-image-agent` could not be loaded (`libnative-image-agent.so` not found). Metrics are also inconsistent with the preserved work: `stats/org.glassfish.jersey.core/jersey-client/2.25.1/execution-metrics.json` records `generated_loc: 0`, `test_file: None`, `metadata_file: None`, and no commit delta even though the generation log shows uncommitted test/metadata files were produced.\n\nPlease inspect:\n- `logs/org.glassfish.jersey.core:jersey-client:2.25.1/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-08T18-18-19-795765Z.log`\n- `logs/org.glassfish.jersey.core:jersey-client:2.25.1/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-08T18-18-19-810557Z.log`\n- `logs/org.glassfish.jersey.core:jersey-client:2.25.1/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-06-08T18-19-15-468208Z.log`\n- `logs/org.glassfish.jersey.core:jersey-client:2.25.1/native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-2026-06-08T18-19-14-426573Z.log`\n\nManual next steps:\n1. Check out the preserved work branch and recover/review the generated `HttpUrlConnectorAnonymous5Test` plus metadata changes from the preserved run artifacts.\n2. Fix the native Jersey bootstrap path, starting with the `JerseyClientBuilder`/`BundleReference` failures, then rerun `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.glassfish.jersey.core:jersey-client:2.25.1`.\n3. Verify the GraalVM environment exposes a working `native-image-agent` (`libnative-image-agent.so`) before rerunning metadata generation or trace-based verification."}}
